About flashable zip builder:

Helps in creating a flashable zip of any kind. Either it is for bootanimation or any app that you want to update via cwm.

Features
-Generate META-INF fore core folder -Fixes permissions -makes a signed/unsigned flashable zip

Requirements
- JDK installed (optional) -this is used to sign zip

- Notepad++ -used to edit updater-script

How to use

-Place your files in fzb/system folder

eg : If you want to make a flashable zip for a font

place your fonts in fzb/system/fonts and use the tool to create a flashabe zip
